phoqa: Phusha noma donsa onyakazayo noma oshintsha ukunyakaza kwento
amandla adonsela phansi: Amandla aheha izinto ngobuningi ziye kwenye
isisindo: Ukuphoqelela okwenziwe entweni ngenxa yamandla adonsela phansi
umsebenzi: Ukudluliswa kwamandla lapho amandla esebenza futhi enyakazisa into
amandla angaba khona: Amandla agciniwe ngenxa yokuma kwento noma ukumiswa
ukungqubuzana: Amandla aphikisana nokunyakaza phakathi kwezindawo ezimbili ezixhumene
umsindo: Uhlobo lwamandla oluhamba njengamagagasi endaweni ethile
